                            <comment id="13476141" author="slebresne" created="Mon, 15 Oct 2012 13:37:44 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hum, I think that is due to some bad merge or something along that way. Basically we were using a column value instead of a key because SelectStatement.buildBound() was used on keys but was (wrongfully) using columns internally instead.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Patch attached to change that and that makes buildBound static to make it harder to do that kind of mistake again.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
